		   <tr><td valign="top" class="mform2" ><span class="fs8"><span class="notbold">By: </span><a href="/db/poster.html?user=64677"><span class="Sage">xaanru</span></a><b><span class="Sage"><br/>Sage</span></b><br /><img src="/shared/user_star_ico.gif" height="9" width="9" alt="*" /><img src="/shared/user_star_ico.gif" height="9" width="9" alt="*"/><img src="/shared/user_star_ico.gif" height="9" width="9" alt="*" /><br />3437 posts
