<td valign="top" class="mform2" width="100%">
<p>If you are going to stand up and hit alot you will need a large mana pool and excellent mana regen. If you don't have those things then you are only hurting your group. They will need healing. Later on the yaulps allow you to regen mana while standing and fighting as well as your sheild spell. Having the extended enhancements help too. Means your hots last alot longer. Once those are taken care of you will need good armor with AC, Dex, AGI etc. Make sure to get that def up too! But really, you need the basics first such as good mana pool and mana regen. Remember to put aa's in increasing your wis cap too when you get to the proper levels. Sucks having lots of wis to only have it capped.</p>
